This is incorrect: the `seeking` event [does return data](https://github.com/vimeo/player.js/#seeking):

```
{
    duration: number
    percent: number
    seconds: number
}
```

Should add `console.log` for test to inspect the returned payload;

```
console.log(data.duration);
console.log(data.percent);
console.log(data.second);
```

